_sText: zm_onadega_v2 Map Features: Cubemaps Radar Map A New Secret New Underground Area Better Looks This is a remake of zm_onadega, as you might guess. This version is mostly scenery changes, but I also added an underground lab area and extended the area around the house for you to play on, though it's still mostly field. I also added 1 new secret, and made the house look more like the actual house. I also added a TV antenna tower that they have at the back. You can climb it as a ladder to get to the roof. All old secrets stayed the same except the hard one under the deck. I also re-did all the terrain around the house, so it looks sexy. *EDIT* The map has now been up to _v2a with 5 minor bug fixes. Questions & Comments are appreciated.
